high_descs: Turn right to face the sink.
Pick up green sponge from sink.
Turn right, proceed to shower.  Turn left to face sink closest to shower stall.
Place sponge on counter to the left of the sink.
Turn left, proceed to sink closest to toilet.  Turn right to face counter between sink and toilet.
Pick up green sponge from back of toilet.
Turn right, go to shower stall.  Turn left and go to sink.
Place sponge to the right of sink in front of pump dispenser.
anns.task_desc: Move two sponges to opposite sides of one sink.

high_descs: Knock the paper roll off of the holder so it falls onto the floor, then turn to face the sink.
Pick up the green sponge from the sink.
Walk over to the empty sink and face it.
Put the green sponge down to the left of the sink.
Turn left and walk to the edge of the counter next to the toilet.
Pickup the green sponge from the top of the toilet.
Turnaround and walk back to the empty sink.
Put the green sponge down to the right of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put both green sponges on either side of the empty sink.

high_descs: Turn to the right and face the sink to your immediate right.
Take the green sponge out of the sink.
Turn to the right, walk toward the wall, and turn to the left and face the sink to your immediate left.
Place the sponge on the front of the counter to the left of the sink.
Turn to the left, walk toward the wall, turn to the right and face the toilet.
Take the green sponge from the back of the toilet tank.
Turn to the right, walk toward the wall, and turn to the left and face the sink to your immediate left.
Place the sponge on the front of the counter to the right of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Move both sponges to either side of the sink furthest from the toilet.
